org.micromanager

Interface AutofocusPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MMGenericPlugin, MMPlugin, org.scijava.plugin.SciJavaPlugin

    public interface AutofocusPlugin
extends MMPlugin
    This interface is used for a java-based autofocus plugin. Properly compiled jars can be added to the mmplugins directory of Micro-Manager and they will be loaded into the autofocus menu. It also wraps autofocus devices implemented in C++ and exposed by the core, so both java and C++ based autofocus plugins can be used by this common interface.
